

{"id":6503,"date":"2024-03-27T13:34:41","date_gmt":"2024-03-27T06:34:41","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/?p=6503"},"modified":"2024-05-01T20:26:07","modified_gmt":"2024-05-01T13:26:07","slug":"9-loi-ich-cua-tap-luyen-voi-suc-khoe-tinh-than","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/9-loi-ich-cua-tap-luyen-voi-suc-khoe-tinh-than\/","title":{"rendered":"9 l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe tinh th\u1ea7n"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6647 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG_7890-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, l\u1ee3i \u00edch\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1829\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG_7890-scaled.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG_7890-300x214.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG_7890-1024x732.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG_7890-768x549.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG_7890-1536x1097.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG_7890-2048x1463.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn ra nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi m\u00e0 n\u00f3 mang l\u1ea1i cho s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe tinh th\u1ea7n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 9 l\u1ee3i \u00edch m\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n mang l\u1ea1i (m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u1ee3i \u00edch trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9 sau v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean).<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><b>9 l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe tinh th\u1ea7n<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea1i sao vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta l\u00e0 ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e3o b\u1ed9 c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 b\u1eafp b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e1c. H\u00e3y t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e3o c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111ang tham gia v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00f3, n\u00f3 s\u1ea3n sinh ra m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u00e1c hormone h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac nh\u01b0 dopamine, endorphin v\u00e0 endocannabinoids, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 lo\u1ea1i kh\u00e1c. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng hormone n\u00e0y gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac sau khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh nh\u1ecbp tim v\u00e0 huy\u1ebft \u00e1p, v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c kh\u00e1c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n? N\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t cho n\u00e3o, v\u00e0 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng t\u1ed1t cho to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 9 l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe tinh th\u1ea7n:<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>1. Gi\u1ea3m c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng<\/b><\/h3>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, khi b\u1ea1n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c v\u1edbi c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 cao, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n. Ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn nh\u1eefng suy ngh\u0129 ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c trong th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tan bi\u1ebfn khi b\u1ea1n t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>2. C\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng tr\u1ea7m c\u1ea3m<\/b><\/h3>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng endorphin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u0103ng c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ng\u1ee5 \u00fd r\u1eb1ng luy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u00e1c tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1ea7m c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>3. Ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n<\/b><\/h3>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7 ngon h\u01a1n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. T\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n gi\u00fap k\u00edch th\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 b\u1eafp v\u00e0 g\u00e2y m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7 theo th\u1eddi gian.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>4. Tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ef1 tin<\/b><\/h3>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u00fap t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin cho b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. Th\u00f3i quen t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1ebd n\u00e2ng cao s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>5. Suy ngh\u0129 l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n<\/b><\/h3>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e0ng d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3, b\u1ea1n c\u00e0ng \u00edt m\u1eafc k\u1eb9t trong nh\u1eefng ki\u1ec3u suy ngh\u0129 ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c. Vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng suy ngh\u0129 tr\u1ea7m ng\u00e2m v\u00e0 c\u00e1c tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng lo l\u1eafng kh\u00e1c.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>6. C\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c<\/b><\/h3>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vi\u1ec7c v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o n\u00e3o.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>7. Gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 m\u1eafc b\u1ec7nh<\/b><\/h3>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">i\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1eadm l\u1ea1i ho\u1eb7c ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u1ec7nh l\u00fd. Th\u00eam v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u0169ng gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e3o h\u00f3a.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>8. T\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/b><\/h3>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vi\u1ec7c l\u1eb7p \u0111i l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n gi\u00fap t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c c\u01a1 quan tr\u00ean c\u01a1 th\u1ec3. V\u00ec v\u1eady, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng cao h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>9. Ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n<\/b><\/h3>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng, c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Th\u00f3i quen v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u00e0y m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng th\u00f3i quen x\u1ea5u.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">The New Gym &#8211; Gym cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&#8211; Email: cskh@thenewgym.vn<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&#8211; Hotline: 1900 63 69 20<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&#8211; Facebook: The New Gym<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; Zalo OA: <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/zalo.me\/thenewgym\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">https:\/\/zalo.me\/thenewgym<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp: <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/phong-gym-gan-day-the-new-gym-gan-day\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/phong-gym-gan-day-the-new-gym-gan-day\/<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>&nbsp; M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng nh\